<I c="Tutorial" i="tutorial" m="tutorials.tutorial" n="tutorial_LiveMode_Needs_ManagingNeeds" s="315410">
  <T n="name">0xC977BE3A<!--String: "Managing Needs"--></T>
  <L n="slides">
    <U>
      <T p="InGame\UI\tutorial\Client\Beginner\Beginner_Needs_1.png" n="image">2f7d0004:00000000:0e510bc12b914501</T>
      <T n="text">0x2E0DBA84<!--String: "Managing your Sim’s <b><font color='#199C2C'>Needs</font></b> is essential to ensure their <b><font color='#199C2C'>happiness</font></b>, <b><font color='#199C2C'>productivity</font></b>, and even <b><font color='#199C2C'>survival</font></b>!\n\nYou can see the current state of your Sim’s Needs in the <b><font color='#199C2C'>Needs panel</font></b>. If you click on a <b><font color='#199C2C'>Need icon</font></b>, your active Sim will try to do something to take care of that Need."--></T>
    </U>
    <U>
      <T n="image" p="InGame\UI\tutorial\Client\LiveMode\LiveMode_ManagingNeeds_2.png">2f7d0004:00000000:8621a57230510beb</T>
      <T n="text">0x178E682<!--String: "More <b><font color='#199C2C'>expensive Objects</font></b> are more <b><font color='#199C2C'>effective</font></b> at fulfilling Sims’ Needs. \n\nYou can check which Need an Object can fulfill, and how efficient it is, in the Object’s <b><font color='#199C2C'>tooltip</font></b> in the <b><font color='#199C2C'>Build catalog</font></b>."--></T>
    </U>
    <U>
      <T n="image" p="InGame\UI\tutorial\Client\LiveMode\LiveMode_ManagingNeeds_3.png">2f7d0004:00000000:8621a57230510bea</T>
      <T n="text">0xDB3D888A<!--String: "Another tip for efficient Needs management is <b><font color='#199C2C'>multitasking</font></b>! Sims can do some things at the same time, such as eating in front of the TV to fulfill their Hunger and Fun needs at the same time.\n\nYou should also consider your Sim’s <b><font color='#199C2C'>Traits</font></b> when managing their Needs. A Bookworm will have more Fun reading, while a Music Lover prefers to listen to music."--></T>
    </U>
  </L>
